commentary: Imran Tahir to Mohammad Hafeez, no run huuuuuge appeal for lbw and not given! Tahir isn't discussing with his captain, he wants a review. This was drifted in, full on off and the googly hits Hafeez's gut/stomach while he tries to sweep. Looked plumb, but umpire Dharmasena wasn't agreeing. Let's see what we have here - replays show no inside-edge, pitching outside off, hitting on middle, but going over leg stump! Great call from the umpire and South Africa lose their review. A wry smile on the umpire's face!
